<template>
  <button @click="logout">Logout</button>
</template>
<script>
import axios from 'axios';
export default {
  methods: {
    async CreatePost() {
      let response = await axios.post("logout", this.data);
    },
    logout() {
      localStorage.removeItem("token");
      this.$router.push("/apiLogin");
    },
  },
};
</script>
